ely ignore this email.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 40px;background-color:#fafafa;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#999999;\">Best regards, Kenya Drylands Investment Hub Team</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>"
